description: Denmark warns the UK that bigger catches in UK waters may not mean bigger sales to the EU.
title: Choppy waters of Brexit threaten Danish fishing
title_page: Choppy waters of Brexit threaten Danish fishing - BBC News
maintext: "My uncle he was a big fisherman in Grimsby. He went from Denmark and he had two boats, and he lived in Grimsby for many years," she says. He did so well in the UK he would visit Denmark in his own plane.
